{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"594896-hello-sun","title":"¡Hola, Sol!","description":"Saluda a las maravillas. Dí '¡Hola!' a los milpiés, ranas, barbets y todo lo que bajo el sol llama a la Tierra, su hogar. Y esto te incluye a ti.","language":"Spanish","langCode":"es","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Némesis Zerga"],"illustrators":["Rajiv Eipe"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"CuenTale Cuentoteca digital","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/594896-hello-sun"},"cover":{"card":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/726226/size3/0ff44e83f3466f1771fe9684c2689aea.jpg","large":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/726226/size6/0ff44e83f3466f1771fe9684c2689aea.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/618975/size6/75a20a1b154ba8e6f495f85136d3f7d1.jpg","text":"2/22","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/618992/size6/64d77d7c37d02d28882cc94eb94efab5.jpg","text":"¡Creac!\nPlip,\nplop,\nplip,\nplop,\nplip,\n¡plop!","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/618950/size6/4d87b76f22f578fb76dc590148a4b20a.jpg","text":"¡Hola, Sol!","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/618951/size6/08d69284a52b6f7cd58445f9848dea8e.jpg","text":"Hola, charco.\nPerdón\nrana…","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/618952/size6/09145af95cb8734f2ce8bdaba02a7622.jpg","text":"¡Hola, babosa!","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/653870/size6/1b9b69a68363a3ee92aee749e4674a1a.jpg","text":"Salaam*, caracol.\n*Saludo islámico que significa “la paz sea contigo”.","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/618954/size6/7373a8360e850c85ebf8bbe6eeee0504.jpg","text":"Buenas tardes, señor milpiés.","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/653871/size6/ae4205559f1a13a187c8100fe37824d1.jpg","text":"Buenas noches, mimosa.","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/618956/size6/cfa4c1dced23206f892087f4a2a9720a.jpg","text":"Tuc,\ntuc,\ntuc,\n﻿tuc,\ntuc,\n¡Tuc!","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/653872/size6/8b13c7df00f0628520a5790df1a759e4.jpg","text":"¿Cómo\nestás,\nhermano\nbarbet?","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/653873/size6/58bc52df0585b8f315faa84d6c4603de.jpg","text":"Saludos,\nseñor araña.\n¡Hola, señora polilla!","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/618959/size6/eea23fe34d5483ce62b2521a175f0792.jpg","text":"Hola,\n¿hay alguien ahí?","words":null},{"n":13,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/618960/size6/a41a3e543fb7a05231ff0568ba3c6719.jpg","text":"Hola, rara,\nblanca, maravillosa\nflor silvestre.","words":null},{"n":14,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/618961/size6/fa02a924b0934588dd43d611923aca0c.jpg","text":"¿Y a TI qué te gustaría ser de mayor, semillita?","words":null},{"n":15,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/618962/size6/c461311de54d1567cc2b27497f58e897.jpg","text":"Hola nido de pájaro sastre con cuatro diminutos huevos rojos… Mantendré una distancia segura para que tus padres no se molesten, ¿vale? Bueno.","words":null},{"n":16,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/618963/size6/12dcc6f907c77d832851451b0e775007.jpg","text":"¿Almorzamos,\npájaros turdoides\ncharlatanes?\nMai,\nmai,\nmai,\nmai,\nmai,\nmai,\nmai,\nmai,\nmai,\nmai,","words":null},{"n":17,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/618964/size6/149dff1d781c4e1ae38f0e71c39f3636.jpg","text":"Hola, extraña criatura con un hocico marrón largo y puntiagudo, y orejas torcidas...","words":null},{"n":18,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/653874/size6/6139075f81194f5fece684ea2a2fafb9.jpg","text":"¡Ataque!","words":null},{"n":19,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/618966/size6/1a803f05041439ae32a23831ac4b0319.jpg","text":"¡Por aquí,\nEXTRAÑA BESTIA!","words":null},{"n":20,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/618991/size6/deb150542769c46b149e5c1d7da1f61d.jpg","text":"Croac,\ncroac\nCri,\ncri,\ncri,\ncri\nmai,\nMai,\nmai,\nmai,\nmai,\nmai,\nmai,\nTuc,\ntuc,\ntuc","words":null},{"n":21,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/618968/size6/90b77667f6328479c844daddf0527bcc.jpg","text":"Hola, ¡monstruo de barro!\n¡Croac!","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":21,"words":145}}